### Adding author
POST https://localhost:5001/api/authors HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "Name":"name_req3",
    "LastName":"last_name_req3",
    "BirthDay":"11/08/1950"
}

###Updating author
POST https://localhost:5001/api/authors/update/7 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "Id":7,
    "Name":"name_req2",
    "LastName":"last_name_req2",
    "BirthDay":"08/08/1980"
}

###Removing author
GET https://localhost:5001/api/authors/remove/2 HTTP/1.1
